Questions answered this week are;

What do I think about cheap ceramic high gain pickups from Amazon?
Why do I use straight headstocks, when some other builders use angled?
Does a two piece body have slightly less resonance then a one piece? General pros and cons of each?
What's my favourite vibrato system?
Why is my workbench so high?
What makes a high end guitar high end?
